    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 2004 BMW M3 (E46) is a mechanically sound driver\u2019s example featuring the high-strung S54 3.2L inline-six engine, renowned for its individual throttle bodies and 8,000 RPM redline. The powertrain is mated to a traditional 6-speed manual gearbox, providing direct engagement through a factory-spec limited-slip differential. Critical preventive maintenance has been addressed, including the reinforcement of the rear subframe mounting points and a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul to ensure optimal variable valve timing. The suspension retains its factory geometry with refreshed bushings and dampers, maintaining the chassis's legendary lateral grip and steering feedback. While showing minor cosmetic patina consistent with spirited use, the vehicle remains structurally rigid and performance-ready for the discerning enthusiast.",
      "price": 32500.0,
