      "description": "This vehicle has been meticulously cared for and remains in impressive shape. The exterior boasts a deep, lustrous finish with only minor road wear consistent with careful driving. Inside, the cabin is clean and smoke-free; the premium upholstery is well-preserved, and every electronic feature\u2014from the intuitive infotainment system to the dual-zone climate control\u2014functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, the car is solid, featuring a smooth-shifting transmission and a responsive engine that has been serviced at all recommended intervals. It sits on a set of high-quality tires with significant tread life remaining. This is a reliable, turn-key car that perfectly balances performance and comfort, ready for its next owner to enjoy immediately.",
